text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It captures the extent to
which people are free from government torture, political killings, and forced labor, they have property rights, and enjoy
the freedoms of movement, religion, expression, and association. The variables ranges from 0 to 1 (most rights).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); Gapminder (v6); HYDE (v3.2); UN (2022)
